@page "/learn"

<PageTitle>Learn | MarketGrowth</PageTitle>

<div class="mg-page">
    <h1>Learn Trading & Markets</h1>
    <p class="mg-subtitle">
        Build your knowledge. Trade with confidence. Grow with purpose.
    </p>

    <section class="mg-section">
        <h2>What is Trading?</h2>
        <p>
            Trading is the act of buying and selling financial assets such as stocks,
            cryptocurrencies, and forex with the goal of making a profit from price movements.
            Successful trading is based on knowledge, discipline, and strategy.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mg-section">
        <h2>Market Analysis</h2>
        <p>
            Traders use two main types of analysis:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Technical Analysis</strong> - studying charts, trends, and indicators.</li>
            <li><strong>Fundamental Analysis</strong> - analyzing news, earnings, and economic data.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mg-section">
        <h2>Risk Management</h2>
        <p>
            Protecting your capital is more important than chasing profits. Always use:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Stop-loss levels</li>
            <li>Position sizing</li>
            <li>Risk-to-reward planning</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mg-section">
        <h2>MarketGrowth Tools</h2>
        <p>
            MarketGrowth helps you track live market data, save favorites, monitor trends,
            and receive alerts based on real-time price movements.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
